quran[1]{c,v,t}:
  9,3,"[This is] an announcement from Allah and His Apostle to all the people on the day of the greater á¸¥ajj: that Allah and His Apostle repudiate the polytheists: If you repent that is better for you; but if you turn your backs [on Allah], know that you cannot thwart Allah, and inform the faithless of a painful punishment"
